    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno nativitatis eius
                        millesimo centesimo sexagesimo octavo, sexto kalendas aprelis, indictione
                        prima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName ref="#people/3226"
                            >Castracane</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3214"
                            >Uberti</persName> et <persName ref="#people/3233">Sindica</persName>
                        mater eius et relicta quondam suprascripti Uberti et <persName><name
                                ref="Iulicta">Iolicta</name></persName> conius eiusdem Castracanis,
                        (…) ubi interfuit notitia <persName key="#Notary #Judge"><name ref="Piculus"
                                >Picculi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/3232">Signa</placeName> et domni imperatoris (…)
                        insimul per hanc cartulam donamus et offerimus tibi deo et <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">hospitali</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">sanctorum Iacobi et
                            Gilii</orgName> de <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Topascio</placeName> unam nostram videlicet petiam de terra que est
                        ortalis et esse videtur in loco <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Roads"
                            >Puteo</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Gratianus">Gratiani</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Nerus">Neri</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Vecchio"
                                >Vechi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Wantarus"
                                >Guantari</name></persName>, et alterum in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, latera ambo detinet in terris suprascripti hospitalis.
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et insuper penam lib.
                        quinquaginta lucensium denariorum et consulum et treuguanorum lucensium
                        presentium et futurorum vel alterius lucane potestatis. (…) Actum in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/3227">Gangalandi</placeName> in domo Castracani.
                        Signum manus suprascriptorum iugalium et Sindiche (…). Hec autem cartula
                        tali tenore est facta si suprascriptus Castracane sine herede filio vel
                        filia de uxore mortuus fuerit, ut suprascripta ecclesia et hospitalis
                        detineat et possideat et usufructuetur suprascriptam terram, donec
                        suprascripte ecclesie et hospitali lib. viginti sex denariorum lucensium
                        date fuerint. (…) Signum manus <persName ref="#people/3229" key="#Witness"
                            >Paltonieri</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3227"
                            >Hughiccionis</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rainuccius">Ranuccini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Teutius">Tiethi</name></persName> filii eius, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Harloctus">Arlocti</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Merlinus">Merlini</name></persName> rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (L) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Bonusfilius">Bonusfilius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> donni imperatoris post traditam complevi et
                        dedi.</ab>
                </div>
